  <brief_title>Effect of the Enteric Hormone Glucagon-Like Peptide (GLP-2) on the Intestinal Blood Flow in Patients With Short Bowel Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>GLP-2 Mediated Increased SMA Blood Flow in Patients With Short Bowel Syndrome</official_title>
